# {{ display_name }}

{{ description }}

This is a fullstack monorepo combining a **Symfony {{ php_version }}** API backend with a **Next.js (Node {{ node_version }})** frontend. Both apps live in the same repository and share TypeScript types through `packages/shared-types`.

