## Environment Variables

### Backend (`apps/api/.env.local`)

```dotenv
APP_ENV=dev
APP_SECRET=change-me-to-a-random-32-char-string

{% if database == "postgresql" %}
DATABASE_URL="postgresql://app:app@127.0.0.1:5432/{{ project_name }}?serverVersion=16&charset=utf8"
{% else %}
DATABASE_URL="mysql://app:app@127.0.0.1:3306/{{ project_name }}?serverVersion=8.0"
{% endif %}

{% if use_auth and auth_method == "jwt" %}
JWT_SECRET_KEY=%kernel.project_dir%/config/jwt/private.pem
JWT_PUBLIC_KEY=%kernel.project_dir%/config/jwt/public.pem
JWT_PASSPHRASE=change-me
JWT_TTL=3600
JWT_REFRESH_TTL=604800
{% endif %}

{% if use_redis %}
REDIS_URL=redis://localhost:6379
{% endif %}

{% if use_rabbitmq %}
MESSENGER_TRANSPORT_DSN=amqp://guest:guest@localhost:5672/%2f/messages
{% endif %}

CORS_ALLOW_ORIGIN='^https?://(localhost|127\.0\.0\.1)(:[0-9]+)?$'
```

### Frontend (`apps/web/.env.local`)

```dotenv
NEXT_PUBLIC_API_URL=http://localhost:8000
{% if use_auth %}
NEXTAUTH_URL=http://localhost:3000
NEXTAUTH_SECRET=change-me-to-a-random-secret
{% endif %}
```

