## Deployment

The two apps are deployed independently but versioned together.

1. **Deploy the API first** - run migrations before the new frontend version is live.
2. **Deploy the frontend** - once the API is healthy.
3. **Never break the API contract** - the frontend relies on stable response shapes.

See [docs/architecture.md](docs/architecture.md) for infrastructure details and [docs/api-contract.md](docs/api-contract.md) for the API contract.

{% if use_ci %}
CI/CD is configured via GitHub Actions. Every push to `main` runs linting and tests for both apps. Merge to `main` triggers deployment.
{% endif %}

